  <summary>Markdown note-taking</summary>
  <description>
    <p>QOwnNotes is the open source (GPL) plain-text file notepad with Markdown support and todo list manager for GNU/Linux, Mac OS X and Windows by Patrizio Bekerle, that (optionally) works together with the notes application of ownCloud or Nextcloud.</p>
  </description>
